Mehak.

784
01:20:51,055 --> 01:20:55,184
If something happens, it's your responsibility.

785
01:21:11,408 --> 01:21:13,410
What the hell happened! Where were you?

786
01:21:13,786 --> 01:21:15,037
Relax, mom!

787
01:21:15,037 --> 01:21:17,581
There was a whole nest of spiders under Manu's bed.

788
01:21:17,873 --> 01:21:18,874
So I panicked.

789
01:21:19,249 --> 01:21:21,251
And you should charge your phone.

790
01:21:21,960 --> 01:21:23,962
Anyway, look what I found.

791
01:21:26,131 --> 01:21:27,299
Unbelievable!

792
01:21:27,925 --> 01:21:28,967
Wow!

793
01:21:29,843 --> 01:21:31,220
Even I have this.

794
01:21:32,387 --> 01:21:33,472
Does that make me a murderer too?

795
01:21:33,472 --> 01:21:34,389
Maybe.

796
01:21:34,389 --> 01:21:38,143
Mehak, I told you to please tell this girl to leave.

797
01:21:38,143 --> 01:21:40,354
Listen, Mehak can have friends other than you as well.

798
01:21:40,354 --> 01:21:41,396
Stop getting so J.

799
01:21:41,396 --> 01:21:43,315
Do you want to put this girl in trouble again?

800
01:21:43,565 --> 01:21:46,026
If you suffer a panic attack, what will she do?

801
01:21:46,026 --> 01:21:48,403
Listen, you don't need to worry about me.

802
01:21:48,403 --> 01:21:50,364
- I can take care of myself. I'm a black belt.
- Right.

803
01:21:50,364 --> 01:21:52,199
And Mehak can never harm me.

804
01:21:52,199 --> 01:21:54,743
What if Malhotra files a police complaint against you?

805
01:21:54,743 --> 01:21:56,036
You broke into his house.

806
01:21:56,036 --> 01:21:58,205
He won't do that, he's guilty.

807
01:21:58,205 --> 01:22:00,833
Oh Mehak, please! This is madness.

808
01:22:01,250 --> 01:22:02,876
Why aren't you helping us?

809
01:22:05,170 --> 01:22:06,964
Now Jiya will help us out.

810
01:22:07,464 --> 01:22:08,590
What?!

811
01:22:10,050 --> 01:22:13,554
Ok, it's written here that to get in touch with the dead.

812
01:22:13,887 --> 01:22:18,267
To make contact, you've to be in the same place where she died.

813
01:22:18,809 --> 01:22:19,810
Check.

814
01:22:20,436 --> 01:22:22,312
And it's written that you need..

815
01:22:22,312 --> 01:22:24,565
...to be in possession of something that belonged to her.

816
01:22:24,815 --> 01:22:27,109
We have Jiya's clothes. Check.

817
01:22:28,819 --> 01:22:30,821
Why are we doing this in the bathroom?

818
01:22:30,821 --> 01:22:34,616
- Mehak said that Jiya died in here.
- Right.

819
01:22:36,743 --> 01:22:37,953
Mehak..

820
01:22:37,953 --> 01:22:40,664
No Nikki, that's Jiya. Can't you tell?

821
01:22:44,585 --> 01:22:45,586
Sorry.

822
01:22:56,930 --> 01:23:01,351
Jiya, we come in peace. We mean no harm.

823
01:23:02,269 --> 01:23:05,355
We're here to listen and help you move on.

824
01:23:05,355 --> 01:23:10,027
Jiya, we come in peace. We mean no harm.

825
01:23:11,612 --> 01:23:13,530
Please talk to us.

826
01:23:16,617 --> 01:23:19,411
Maybe Jiya isn't in a mood to talk.

827
01:23:20,162 --> 01:23:22,623
That's because your energy is very negative.

828
01:23:22,623 --> 01:23:23,874
Sure, its always my fault..

829
01:23:24,583 --> 01:23:25,667
Please keep quiet.

830
01:23:26,877 --> 01:23:28,212
We'll try again.

831
01:23:32,382 --> 01:23:34,134
Jiya, please talk to me.

832
01:23:35,510 --> 01:23:37,804
What happened to you in this house?

833
01:23:39,514 --> 01:23:41,767
We're here to help you. Please talk to us

834
01:23:44,102 --> 01:23:45,103
Where are you..

835
01:24:28,522 --> 01:24:29,648
What the hell!

836
01:24:31,525 --> 01:24:34,528
- Jiya tell us who killed you?
- What nonsense! Who are you people?

837
01:24:35,821 --> 01:24:37,531
What's all this? Have you all gone mad?

838
01:24:37,531 --> 01:24:38,615
You're alive?

839
01:24:38,615 --> 01:24:40,033
Of course, I'm alive.

840
01:24:40,325 --> 01:24:42,411
- You're supposed to be dead.
- What?!

841
01:24:42,953 --> 01:24:45,289
Why is she wearing my uniform?

842
01:24:45,956 --> 01:24:49,459
- And you have my ring.
- Sorry.. I'm Shaan, I can explain.

843
01:24:50,127 --> 01:24:51,545
Please explain, Shaan.

844
01:24:53,255 --> 01:24:55,966
Actually, I can't explain but..

845
01:24:55,966 --> 01:24:57,092
What?

846
01:25:00,137 --> 01:25:01,471
Did you call up my parents?

847
01:25:02,306 --> 01:25:04,224
Huh! Are you mad?

848
01:25:05,183 --> 01:25:08,186
Do you know how troubled my parents were after hearing your message?

849
01:25:09,438 --> 01:25:10,897
Who does such a thing!

850
01:25:10,897 --> 01:25:14,067
'I know who killed your daughter.' Manu made you say that?

851
01:25:14,067 --> 01:25:15,902
No, We thought Manu murdered you.

852
01:25:15,902 --> 01:25:19,156
- I've overheard your fights..
- Shut up, you nosey rat! I'm gonna kill Manu!

853
01:25:40,177 --> 01:25:42,929
- Jiya, you're back!
- Get off me! Stay away from me, you sicko!

854
01:25:42,929 --> 01:25:44,556
Don't you understand it's over?

855
01:25:44,556 --> 01:25:46,641
I don't want your grandma's rotten ring!

856
01:25:47,392 --> 01:25:48,852
- Stay away or I'll call the cops.
- Jiya..

857
01:25:48,852 --> 01:25:50,687
- Jiya, it's for you.
- I don't want it.

858
01:25:50,687 --> 01:25:52,230
What did you tell them about us?

859
01:25:52,230 --> 01:25:53,774
Don't listen to them.

860
01:25:53,774 --> 01:25:55,650
They're all mental. I love you.

861
01:25:55,650 --> 01:25:56,651
- No, you don't.
- Please come back.

862
01:25:56,651 --> 01:25:57,861
You hit me. - I'm sorry.

863
01:25:58,153 --> 01:25:59,571
- Please calm down.
- No, I won't.

864
01:25:59,571 --> 01:26:01,656
Sorry, I shouldn't have hit you.

865
01:26:01,656 --> 01:26:03,158
Too late for-sorry now.

866
01:26:03,158 --> 01:26:05,911
You know, I've done an advanced course in laughter therapy.

867
01:26:07,496 --> 01:26:08,497
Shut up!

868
01:26:08,497 --> 01:26:10,916
- I don't get angry anymore, see.
- Shut up!

869
01:26:12,459 --> 01:26:15,462
What do you want? You want to continue flying?

870
01:26:15,462 --> 01:26:18,256
No problem. You don't want to marry me? No problem.

871
01:26:18,507 --> 01:26:20,175
You don't want kids? No problem.

872
01:26:20,509 --> 01:26:22,344
You want to work with other guys?

873
01:26:23,428 --> 01:26:24,888
No problem.

874
01:26:24,888 --> 01:26:26,932
You don't want this ring now? Ok.

875
01:26:27,182 --> 01:26:29,810
I'll put it in my pocket. I'll try later.

876
01:26:30,435 --> 01:26:33,146
I love you, baby. Just come back.

877
01:26:33,146 --> 01:26:35,357
Get off! What are you doing?

878
01:26:35,357 --> 01:26:37,442
Please.. please, I'm sorry.

879
01:26:37,442 --> 01:26:39,945
I won't be stupid again. Come back, please.

880
01:26:40,195 --> 01:26:41,780
I hate you.

881
01:26:41,780 --> 01:26:42,781
I know.

882
01:26:50,163 --> 01:26:52,332
- If you laugh again, I'll slap you.
- I won't laugh.

883
01:27:03,593 --> 01:27:07,055
I have seen her in the bathroom, Shaan.

884
01:27:08,306 --> 01:27:09,349
In the bedroom.

885
01:27:10,809 --> 01:27:11,852
All over the house.

886
01:27:12,894 --> 01:27:14,187
But she's alive.

887
01:27:16,440 --> 01:27:17,816
Why don't you say something?

888
01:27:17,816 --> 01:27:19,276
Mehak, I believe in you.

889
01:27:19,276 --> 01:27:21,069
There's definitely something wrong with this house.

890
01:27:21,069 --> 01:27:23,029
Maybe it wasn't runaway Jiya but..

891
01:27:23,029 --> 01:27:25,490
...how do we now communicate with the real ghost?

892
01:27:25,490 --> 01:27:29,035
- We don't even have their clothes.
- Go home, Nikki. That's enough!

893
01:27:31,163 --> 01:27:32,164
Go home.

894
01:27:34,332 --> 01:27:35,667
And thank you for everything.

895
01:27:35,667 --> 01:27:36,918
Hey, what thank you?

896
01:27:37,169 --> 01:27:39,087
Say that when we catch the ghost.

897
01:27:39,337 --> 01:27:40,422
Happy Diwali.

898
01:27:49,389 --> 01:27:51,558
Are you going to send me to mental hospital now?

899
01:27:53,185 --> 01:27:54,186
What?!

900
01:27:55,145 --> 01:27:56,313
No, M, never.

901
01:28:01,485 --> 01:28:05,822
I've never seen a more stronger girl than you all my life.

902
01:28:07,824 --> 01:28:11,244
You will be fine, I promise, just don't give up.

903
01:28:19,169 --> 01:28:20,504
Reality or imagination..

904
01:28:21,296 --> 01:28:24,674
Right or wrong, I can't tell difference.

905
01:28:27,093 --> 01:28:28,345
I'm crazy.

906
01:28:29,763 --> 01:28:31,973
- Please go.
- I'm not going anywhere, Mehak.

907
01:28:33,183 --> 01:28:34,226
I love you.

908
01:28:35,519 --> 01:28:36,853
I've always loved you.

909
01:28:42,192 --> 01:28:44,778
I'm so sorry.

910
01:29:23,191 --> 01:29:25,110
I hate your hands.

911
01:29:28,071 --> 01:29:30,532
Your touch disgusts me.

912
01:29:33,034 --> 01:29:34,744
Your hands are dirty..

913
01:29:42,544 --> 01:29:43,962
...ugly

914
01:29:51,511 --> 01:29:53,221
You've lost your mind.

915
01:29:55,640 --> 01:29:56,641
Not me.

916
01:29:59,894 --> 01:30:01,563
You need treatment, not me.

917
01:30:05,942 --> 01:30:07,110
Scoundrel..

918
01:30:08,445 --> 01:30:10,864
- How dare you stare at me!
- M?

919
01:30:11,906 --> 01:30:17,245
Who gave you the right to touch me?

920
01:30:19,205 --> 01:30:20,957
It's you who stinks

921
01:30:32,135 --> 01:30:33,928
Because you're rotten.

922
01:30:35,680 --> 01:30:39,142
I'm not wrong, you are.

923
01:30:40,810 --> 01:30:42,062
Wicked.

924
01:30:43,229 --> 01:30:46,483
Evil. Filthy.

925
01:30:51,112 --> 01:30:52,238
Sick.

926
01:30:54,908 --> 01:30:55,909
Why did you do it?

927
01:30:56,451 --> 01:30:57,869
- What did you gain?
- Will you stop it?

928
01:30:57,869 --> 01:31:00,955
- Do you know whom you're talking to?
- I'm talking to you, Shaan.

929
01:31:00,955 --> 01:31:03,917
You just don't understand me!

930
01:31:06,419 --> 01:31:09,172
You tell me to be brave.

931
01:31:10,173 --> 01:31:12,217
Go out. Go where?

932
01:31:13,635 --> 01:31:17,263
You told me, I wasn't raped.

933
01:31:18,932 --> 01:31:21,226
Should I have been raped?- Enough!

934
01:31:22,268 --> 01:31:25,313
If you touch me again, I'll call the cops.

935
01:31:25,313 --> 01:31:28,233
- Go ahead, call them over.
- You are Disgusting!

936
01:31:28,233 --> 01:31:30,443
The more people see this drama, the better it will be

937
01:31:31,027 --> 01:31:34,114
I took you as my friend and what did you do the moment you got a
chance!

938
01:31:34,447 --> 01:31:36,032
How are you any different from him?

939
01:31:36,324 --> 01:31:37,909
How dare you say that!

940
01:31:37,909 --> 01:31:39,035
What about all the stress you've been..

941
01:31:39,035 --> 01:31:40,245
...putting me through over the past three years?

942
01:31:40,245 --> 01:31:42,288
We're friends today, lovers tomorrow, who knows what we are the day
after!

943
01:31:42,288 --> 01:31:43,790
Make up your bloody mind!

944
01:31:44,958 --> 01:31:46,960
I've done so much for you.

945
01:31:46,960 --> 01:31:48,253
I'm going to call Anu.

946
01:31:48,253 --> 01:31:50,171
I'm talking to you, you freak.

947
01:31:51,548 --> 01:31:53,758
M.. M..

948
01:31:54,092 --> 01:31:57,178
M, please.. that's enough!

949
01:32:16,573 --> 01:32:17,615
Oh god!

950
01:32:18,491 --> 01:32:19,951
M..

951
01:32:23,371 --> 01:32:25,957
I'm sorry, M. Are you hurt? Let me check

952
01:32:25,957 --> 01:32:28,084
- Stop it.
- Help!

953
01:32:28,084 --> 01:32:29,169
Get away from me!

954
01:32:31,045 --> 01:32:32,130
M..

955
01:32:32,422 --> 01:32:33,423
Oh my god!

956
01:32:35,884 --> 01:32:37,051
Oh my god!

957
01:32:40,555 --> 01:32:42,307
Stay away from me!

958
01:32:42,307 --> 01:32:44,851
I'm not mad, you'll kill me.

959
01:32:45,185 --> 01:32:47,437
It wasn't Jiya, it was me. I was seeing myself. I won't let you kill
me.

960
01:32:47,437 --> 01:32:48,646
What are you saying, Mehak?

961
01:32:48,646 --> 01:32:50,648
Drop that blade, you'll hurt yourself.

962
01:32:50,648 --> 01:32:52,275
I saw all of this!

963
01:32:56,446 --> 01:32:58,072
Drop the blade, M!

964
01:32:58,072 --> 01:33:00,784
- No.
- M, drop the blade.

965
01:33:20,595 --> 01:33:21,638
Look at me.

966
01:33:34,651 --> 01:33:36,152
Look at me.

967
01:33:36,820 --> 01:33:40,281
M, I'm going to take you to the hospital. Look at me.

968
01:33:41,449 --> 01:33:43,284
M..

969
01:33:50,500 --> 01:33:51,501
Let's..

970
01:33:52,669 --> 01:33:53,753
The ice box..

971
01:33:56,047 --> 01:33:58,466
I'll be right back..wait..

972
01:35:38,107 --> 01:35:40,735
- Hi, Mehak was..
- Nikki, do you know what time it is?

973
01:35:40,735 --> 01:35:43,529
- I know, sorry but I got a call from Mehak.
- She's sleeping.

974
01:35:43,529 --> 01:35:46,449
I just thought it's something urgent.

975
01:35:46,449 --> 01:35:49,077
It's alright, she's sleeping. I'm here, go home.

976
01:35:49,494 --> 01:35:51,496
Just tell her..

977
01:35:51,913 --> 01:35:53,164
What was that?

978
01:35:54,958 --> 01:35:57,502
Maybe the cat entered.

979
01:35:58,461 --> 01:36:01,255
Cat? Gul aunty's cat is back?

980
01:36:01,255 --> 01:36:02,840
She keeps coming in through the window.

981
01:36:02,840 --> 01:36:04,384
Yes, I have to go now..

982
01:36:08,429 --> 01:36:09,389
Nikki, go home.

983
01:36:09,389 --> 01:36:10,431
- What's that?
- Over here.

984
01:36:10,431 --> 01:36:11,683
What? - On your...

985
01:36:11,683 --> 01:36:12,850
It's nothing, Nikki. Go home.

986
01:36:13,267 --> 01:36:15,687
- No, I have to meet Mehak.
- I'm telling you she's sleeping. Go home.

987
01:36:15,687 --> 01:36:17,146
I don't believe you, Shaan.

988
01:36:17,146 --> 01:36:18,147
What do you mean you don't believe me?

989
01:36:18,147 --> 01:36:20,525
- She's sleeping, I can't wake her up.
- I'm not going.

990
01:36:20,525 --> 01:36:22,068
- If she's sleeping, wake her up.
- Just relax.

991
01:36:22,068 --> 01:36:23,319
- Nikki..
- I won't leave without meeting her.

992
01:36:23,319 --> 01:36:25,113
Have you lost it? Don't you understand?

993
01:36:25,113 --> 01:36:27,532
- Nikki, get out.
- Not without meeting..

994
01:36:29,075 --> 01:36:30,451
- Mehak!
- Nikki!

995
01:36:37,250 --> 01:36:39,752
- What have you done?
- I haven't done anything, Nikki.

996
01:36:39,752 --> 01:36:41,754
- She fell in the bathroom.
- Liar!

997
01:36:41,754 --> 01:36:43,339
I swear, Nikki. I'm not lying.

998
01:36:43,339 --> 01:36:45,049
It was an accident, I swear.

999
01:36:45,049 --> 01:36:47,093
Mehak, I'm calling my dad.

1000
01:36:47,552 --> 01:36:49,220
Everything will be fine.

1001
01:36:50,763 --> 01:36:52,849
- Nikki, listen to me.
- No.

1002
01:36:53,099 --> 01:36:54,559
- It was an accident, I swear.
- No.

1003
01:36:54,559 --> 01:36:55,893
No! - Give me the phone.

1004
01:36:55,893 --> 01:36:58,354
- Give me the phone! Let go!
- No!

1005
01:36:59,313 --> 01:37:01,899
Leave it! Let me call the ambulance.

1006
01:37:09,073 --> 01:37:11,034
Stop it!

1007
01:37:15,288 --> 01:37:17,874
No, no.. Nikki.. Nikki!

1008
01:37:18,374 --> 01:37:21,252
Nikki, wake up!

1009
01:37:21,502 --> 01:37:23,755
Mehak, she's alive. We need to take her to the hospital.

1010
01:37:24,213 --> 01:37:25,214
Mehak?

1011
01:37:26,674 --> 01:37:27,759
Mehak?

1012
01:37:41,856 --> 01:37:42,857
Mehak..

1013
01:38:34,325 --> 01:38:35,743
Mehak! Hey!

1014
01:38:37,036 --> 01:38:38,371
Mehak, open the door.

1015
01:38:39,163 --> 01:38:40,832
Mehak, open the door.

1016
01:38:43,292 --> 01:38:45,253
Mehak, open the door. What are you doing?!

1017
01:38:45,628 --> 01:38:47,421
Why are you afraid of me, Mehak?

1018
01:38:49,465 --> 01:38:50,925
Why are you running away from me?

1019
01:38:52,510 --> 01:38:54,137
Your fight is not with me, Mehak.

1020
01:38:55,179 --> 01:38:56,389
It's with your self.

1021
01:38:58,474 --> 01:39:00,476
I know you're standing outside, Mehak.

1022
01:39:05,106 --> 01:39:06,566
I won't do anything now.

1023
01:39:08,818 --> 01:39:10,236
I'm tired.

1024
01:39:12,155 --> 01:39:14,073
I'm so tired.

1025
01:39:30,965 --> 01:39:32,633
You need to get to the hospital, princess.

1026
01:39:37,138 --> 01:39:38,681
And your finger's in the freezer.

1027
01:39:53,196 --> 01:39:57,241
Ma'am, I'm calling from B-603, Overlook Apartments.

1028
01:39:57,241 --> 01:39:58,284
Malad East.

1029
01:39:59,535 --> 01:40:01,913
I need an ambulance, it's a medical emergency.

